    </p>

    <p>If, at your request, we provide additional services for you, such as travel or
    hotel bookings or the organisation of child care, we transmit the data to the
    recipients required for the respective service provision. These can be in
    particular: Hotels, travel agencies, the Federal Foreign Office, other
